== About ==

Gridpulse is used by the Grid Australia project to help monitor status to grid gateway machines. It reports information via email back to a central server located at. http://goc.gridaus.org.au/

== Install ==

Gridpulse should be run using a scheduler like cron

Example:
3,23,43 * * * * /usr/local/bin/gridpulse grid_pulse@gridaus.org.au >/dev/null 2>&1

